<note id="fs-idm243198896" class="os-teacher">
<title>Standards</title>
<para id="fs-idm244656304"><emphasis effect="bold">Topic</emphasis>: 7.13 World War II: Military</para>
<para id="fs-idm215465664"><emphasis effect="bold">Theme</emphasis>: WOR America in the World</para>
<para id="fs-idm242756240"><emphasis effect="bold">Learning Objective</emphasis>: Unit 7M Explain the causes and effects of the victory of the United States and its allies over the Axis Powers</para>
<para id="fs-idm198553200"><emphasis effect="bold">Historical Development</emphasis>: 7.3.III.D</para>
